data.description: PRICE REDUCED!   AND  Seller will give an $8,000 credit to buyer at closing for A/C and flooring!!!  This 3 Bedroom/2 Bath/2 Car Garage home sits on a spacious lot, located in the Meadow Ridge of Grand Island Subdivision. This home features an open concept with a well-appointed kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a bar that overlooks the Living/Dining Room.  The home also offers a split bedroom plan and interior laundry closet.  The subdivision sits right between Eustis, Tavares & Leesburg.  The home is close to shopping, dining, entertainment, and attractions in the Orlando area. It is also within driving distance to everything the Central Florida area has to offer.  Low HOA, amenities include community green space, playground, recreation area with picnic table and pavilion.  This home is energy efficient with solar panels in place.  Home needs TLC and air conditioning system needs replaced.
